sections.Trivia:
- The names of the suspects come from "flower viewing" (花見 ,hanami?)[1] :
Tohei Benzaki (弁崎 桐平) comes from "bento" (弁当) ;
Ikuyo Yatani (矢谷 郁代) comes from "stalls" (屋台 ,yatai?) ;
Yoriko Danno (段野 頼子) comes from "dango" (団子) ;
Shigemori Sakamaki (坂巻 重守) comes from "drinking parties" (酒盛り ,sakamori?).
